doc.after: The Lethbridge School District No. 51 and the separate Holy Spirit Roman Catholic School Division administer grades kindergarten through 12 locally. The Palliser School Division, which is based in Lethbridge, administers public primary and secondary education in the outlying areas. Lethbridge School District No. 51 administers three high schools (Chinook High School, Lethbridge Collegiate Institute, and Winston Churchill High School), four middle schools, and 12 elementary schools in Lethbridge.
